	<section class="b" id="srandblock-content">
		<ul>
<li>

	
	<a href="//slashdot.org/submission/17306057/source-code-to-infocoms-text-adventure-interpreters-now-available?utm_source=rss1.0&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;sbsrc=firehose">
		Source Code to Infocom's Text Adventure Interpreters Now Available
	</a>
</li><li>

	
	<a href="//slashdot.org/submission/17306003/fcc-tightens-telco-rules-to-combat-sim-swapping?utm_source=rss1.0&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;sbsrc=firehose">
		FCC Tightens Telco Rules to Combat SIM-Swapping
